HEADWORD: Pawnbroker
<hw>Pawn"bro`ker</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who makes a
business of lending money on the security of personal property pledged
or deposited in his keeping.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

